---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure — AI Creator Stack"
  description="How AI Creator Stack uses affiliate links and how it affects our reviews."
  canonicalPath="/affiliate-disclosure"
>
  <div class="container prose">
    <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: July 2026</em></p>

    <p>
      AI Creator Stack (<strong>theaicreatorstack.com</strong>) is a reader-supported website. To keep
      our reviews free and independent, we participate in affiliate programs — including PartnerStack
      and individual software affiliate programs run by the tools we review.
    </p>

    <h2>What this means</h2>
    <p>
      When you click certain links on our Site and subscribe to or purchase a product, we may earn a
      commission from the vendor. <strong>This comes at no additional cost to you</strong> — you pay the
      same price you would by going directly to the vendor.
    </p>

    <h2>Our commitment to you</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Affiliate relationships <strong>never</strong> determine which tools we feature, how we rank them, or the ratings we give.</li>
      <li>We recommend tools based on hands-on testing and genuine suitability for creators.</li>
      <li>We clearly mark outbound affiliate links, and they use appropriate <code>rel</code> attributes.</li>
      <li>Where a tool has no affiliate program, we still review it on merit if it's relevant to creators.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Pricing accuracy</h2>
    <p>
      SaaS pricing changes frequently. We date-stamp every review with the day we last verified its
      pricing, but we always encourage you to confirm the current price on the tool's official website
      before subscribing.
    </p>

    <h2>Questions?</h2>
    <p>
      If you have any questions about our affiliate relationships, email
      <a href="mailto:info@theaicreatorstack.com">info@theaicreatorstack.com</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
